sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Open message details
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/channels/{channelId}/messages/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    API->>DB: Check access and load message
    DB-->>API: Message found
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + message
    Frontend-->>User: Display message details
